Data Ingestion Report

From iDigBio
Jump to: navigation, search

This is a manually edited (by humans), static representation of the progress of ingestion into iDigBio's portal. This page holds a history of on-boarding new providers.

In order to reduce double data entry, we have removed the Mobilization, Negotiating, and Pre-negotiating queues from this dashboard. Those queues have been tracked in an internal ticket system for some time and manually updating this page to try to keep it in sync no longer seems like a good use of resources.

Information about ingested datasets from data publishers (including record counts, etc.) can be found at the iDigBio Publishers Page:

http://www.idigbio.org/portal/publishers

Note: The Redmine links below go to iDigBio's internal ticketing system and require a login. In most cases, you will want to visit the Publishers Page mentioned directly above.
